I think we can make this patch easier by using actual emojis instead of dealing with mojibake in the console output. Maybe it’s simpler to just replace the whole endpoint block with a new one using visible lines, so we avoid hidden issues. I could use actual emojis like 🧬 and ✅. We should definitely add constants above REDOX_SYSTEM_PROMPT before replacing the endpoint block. Let’s move forward with that!
codex
